==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From the same as [[ἀριστον]] {{GG|712}} and [[βουλή]] {{GG|1012}}; best counselling; 

===Pronunciation===
*Ἀριστόβουλος / Aristoboulos / ar-is-tob'-oo-los

===Proper noun===
'''Ἀριστόβουλος'''

# Aristoboulus, a Christian: - [[Aristobulus]].

